578
00:25:45,440 --> 00:25:47,770
planning to go back to work at the factory?

579
00:25:48,560 --> 00:25:49,800
Didn't they suspend me?

580
00:25:49,800 --> 00:25:51,440
The factory manager wants to make things difficult for me.

581
00:25:51,440 --> 00:25:52,560
I'll just wait and see.

582
00:25:52,560 --> 00:25:53,680
The manager.

583
00:25:53,680 --> 00:25:55,480
How did they give you a hard time?

584
00:25:56,720 --> 00:25:59,520
I think the factory director was merciful enough to you.

585
00:25:59,520 --> 00:26:02,520
If I were the director, I would have fired you already.

586
00:26:03,480 --> 00:26:05,340
It wouldn't go that far, would it?

587
00:26:05,520 --> 00:26:06,560
Why wouldn't it?

588
00:26:07,280 --> 00:26:09,240
Are you just waiting for

589
00:26:09,240 --> 00:26:11,170
the factory to beg you to come back?

590
00:26:11,280 --> 00:26:12,240
What else can I do?

591
00:26:12,240 --> 00:26:13,900
And then you just mess around.

592
00:26:14,840 --> 00:26:16,840
You're over 30 years old

593
00:26:16,840 --> 00:26:18,700
and you've ended up in detention.

594
00:26:18,880 --> 00:26:20,880
What kind of person is Huo Dongfeng?

595
00:26:21,280 --> 00:26:23,280
How could you hang out with him?

596
00:26:24,240 --> 00:26:25,560
Dad, he's not a bad person.

597
00:26:25,560 --> 00:26:26,560
So the government

598
00:26:26,560 --> 00:26:28,960
just wrongfully accuses innocent people?

599
00:26:29,520 --> 00:26:31,200
He's been in labor reform so many times

600
00:26:31,200 --> 00:26:34,160
he's spent more time inside than outside.

601
00:26:34,840 --> 00:26:36,970
Go ahead and keep hanging out with him.

602
00:26:37,560 --> 00:26:38,320
I won't, I won't.

603
00:26:38,320 --> 00:26:40,250
I'll stay away from him from now on.

604
00:26:40,720 --> 00:26:42,480
During those 20 hours inside,

605
00:26:42,480 --> 00:26:44,280
I've already planned my future.

606
00:26:45,440 --> 00:26:46,440
Let's hear it.

607
00:26:47,320 --> 00:26:48,720
I want to become a lawyer.

608
00:26:51,600 --> 00:26:53,130
You want to become a lawyer?

609
00:26:54,000 --> 00:26:56,760
Have you ever studied law for even one day?

610
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:58,000
I studied for two days

611
00:26:58,000 --> 00:27:00,660
learning criminal law at Huo Dongfeng's place.

612
00:27:01,240 --> 00:27:02,700
Look at the place you chose

613
00:27:03,080 --> 00:27:04,800
and the teacher you found.

614
00:27:07,320 --> 00:27:08,780
It's because I know the law

615
00:27:09,080 --> 00:27:10,680
that this time when I went in,

616
00:27:10,680 --> 00:27:12,760
I got out so quickly.

617
00:27:14,560 --> 00:27:16,220
I discussed the law with them,

618
00:27:16,720 --> 00:27:18,250
and they saw I knew my stuff,

619
00:27:18,320 --> 00:27:19,080
so they said, 'Fine,

620
00:27:19,080 --> 00:27:19,960
you can go.'

621
00:27:20,920 --> 00:27:22,720
So that's why they released you?

622
00:27:22,960 --> 00:27:24,160
Then I really misunderstood, Dad.

623
00:27:24,160 --> 00:27:25,840
I thought we paid a 2,000 yuan fine

624
00:27:25,840 --> 00:27:26,970
to get him released.

625
00:27:27,240 --> 00:27:27,960
If that's the case,

626
00:27:27,960 --> 00:27:29,280
let's ask for our money back.

627
00:27:29,280 --> 00:27:30,160
If you know the law so well,

628
00:27:30,160 --> 00:27:31,080
why did we need to pay anything?

629
00:27:31,080 --> 00:27:31,760
Right?

630
00:27:32,000 --> 00:27:32,400
No way.

631
00:27:32,920 --> 00:27:33,720
What are you doing?

632
00:27:33,720 --> 00:27:35,520
Why are you getting so worked up?

633
00:27:36,000 --> 00:27:37,440
You don't understand the law.

634
00:27:37,440 --> 00:27:39,480
That 2,000 yuan had to be paid.

635
00:27:39,840 --> 00:27:41,760
I just meant that by discussing the law with them,

636
00:27:41,760 --> 00:27:43,520
my release went more smoothly.

637
00:27:43,520 --> 00:27:44,680
That's what I meant.

638
00:27:45,480 --> 00:27:46,760
You still want money?

639
00:27:48,320 --> 00:27:50,050
I've been thinking carefully.

640
00:27:50,240 --> 00:27:52,440
In my current profession,

641
00:27:52,440 --> 00:27:54,000
I've hit a bottleneck.

642
00:27:54,200 --> 00:27:55,800
I can't advance any further,

643
00:27:55,840 --> 00:27:57,700
so I might as well change careers.

644
00:28:01,720 --> 00:28:02,240
Dad.

645
00:28:06,720 --> 00:28:07,800
Why are you shaking your leg?

646
00:28:07,800 --> 00:28:09,160
He's just full. It's nothing.

647
00:28:09,160 --> 00:28:09,800
Hurry up and eat.

648
00:28:09,800 --> 00:28:11,080
We'll go home after dinner.

649
00:28:11,080 --> 00:28:12,160
Give me 100 yuan.

650
00:28:12,760 --> 00:28:13,480
What do you need money for?

651
00:28:13,480 --> 00:28:15,080
To buy books for the bar exam.

652
00:28:17,240 --> 00:28:18,400
You're really going to take it?

653
00:28:18,400 --> 00:28:21,080
Of course, we've known each other for over ten years.

654
00:28:21,080 --> 00:28:22,280
Although sometimes I'm really

655
00:28:22,280 --> 00:28:23,740
not... not very reliable.

656
00:28:24,240 --> 00:28:25,200
But my learning ability,

657
00:28:25,200 --> 00:28:26,480
you know it well, right?

658
00:28:26,480 --> 00:28:27,480
If I want to learn something,

659
00:28:27,480 --> 00:28:29,810
I'll definitely master it and excel at it.

660
00:28:29,960 --> 00:28:30,800
Just 100 yuan.

661
00:28:30,800 --> 00:28:32,280
I won't ask for a penny more.

662
00:28:32,280 --> 00:28:33,140
Give me a break.

663
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:35,060
I won't give you a single cent.

664
00:28:35,240 --> 00:28:36,640
If you don't give it to me,

665
00:28:37,920 --> 00:28:39,560
then I'll have to beg you.

666
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:41,280
Go ahead.

667
00:28:44,680 --> 00:28:46,010
I'll kneel down for you.

668
00:28:46,480 --> 00:28:48,440
Fine. How much?

669
00:28:48,960 --> 00:28:50,560
100. Stop playing dumb.

670
00:28:54,600 --> 00:28:55,800
Is Dalei inside?

671
00:28:55,800 --> 00:28:56,800
He's doing fine.

672
00:28:57,760 --> 00:28:59,760
Don't worry. Nobody's hurting him.

673
00:29:00,040 --> 00:29:01,170
Everything's good.

674
00:29:02,560 --> 00:29:03,560
And another thing,

675
00:29:03,560 --> 00:29:05,760
we need to trust in the justice system.

676
00:29:06,120 --> 00:29:06,880
The real culprit

677
00:29:06,880 --> 00:29:08,540
will be found sooner or later.

678
00:29:10,120 --> 00:29:10,880
Also,

679
00:29:11,240 --> 00:29:12,960
I'm studying law now.

680
00:29:13,760 --> 00:29:14,890
When the time comes,

681
00:29:15,240 --> 00:29:17,760
I can personally defend Dalei.

682
00:29:18,120 --> 00:29:19,720
So please don't worry.

683
00:29:21,360 --> 00:29:22,800
It's all right, uncle.

684
00:29:25,280 --> 00:29:27,400
Didn't I give you over 1,000 yuan?

685
00:29:27,400 --> 00:29:29,600
Why are you eating such plain food?

686
00:29:44,320 --> 00:29:45,160
Uncle.

687
00:29:45,640 --> 00:29:46,600
I'm here for you.

688
00:29:47,520 --> 00:29:48,280
Don't worry.

689
00:29:55,560 --> 00:29:56,320
Xiaoxue.

690
00:29:57,880 --> 00:29:59,010
No rush. Eat slowly.

691
00:30:00,160 --> 00:30:01,760
Whenever you're hungry in the future,

692
00:30:01,760 --> 00:30:02,800
just come here.

693
00:30:03,800 --> 00:30:05,200
Order whatever you want.

694
00:30:07,640 --> 00:30:09,970
Your father is definitely not a murderer.

695
00:30:10,400 --> 00:30:11,930
He will surely be released.

696
00:30:13,760 --> 00:30:14,600
No, no.

697
00:30:14,600 --> 00:30:15,480
Eat slowly.

698
00:30:15,480 --> 00:30:16,000
Child,

699
00:30:16,240 --> 00:30:17,200
I'll pay for you.

700
00:30:18,320 --> 00:30:19,180
Take your time.

701
00:30:26,800 --> 00:30:28,120
Remember this girl.

702
00:30:28,120 --> 00:30:29,960
Whatever she orders when she comes here,

703
00:30:29,960 --> 00:30:32,080
make sure she gets plenty of good food.

704
00:30:32,080 --> 00:30:33,240
Just put it on my tab.

705
00:30:33,400 --> 00:30:34,080
Um,

706
00:30:34,720 --> 00:30:36,760
is she that buddy of yours' daughter?

707
00:30:36,760 --> 00:30:38,040
Yes, that's right.

708
00:30:38,320 --> 00:30:40,720
The one you sent kidneys and chives to.

709
00:30:41,960 --> 00:30:43,240
How is he now?

710
00:30:44,560 --> 00:30:45,320
As you said,

711
00:30:45,320 --> 00:30:46,320
he's back in jail.

712
00:30:46,400 --> 00:30:47,240
What a shame.

713
00:30:47,920 --> 00:30:49,360
That thing about the advertisement,

714
00:30:49,360 --> 00:30:51,080
I didn't see the interview.

715
00:30:51,560 --> 00:30:52,400
This time,

716
00:30:52,600 --> 00:30:54,060
he's suspected of murder.

717
00:30:54,440 --> 00:30:55,520
The verdict won't come quickly,

718
00:30:55,520 --> 00:30:57,400
and he won't be released soon either.

719
00:30:57,400 --> 00:30:57,680
Eat.

720
00:30:58,040 --> 00:30:59,240
Did he kill someone after eating those kidneys?

721
00:30:59,240 --> 00:31:00,440
The next day.

722
00:31:00,440 --> 00:31:01,760
It has nothing to do with my kidneys, right?

723
00:31:01,760 --> 00:31:02,840
Hard to say.

724
00:31:03,040 --> 00:31:04,320
This stuff takes time to digest,

725
00:31:04,320 --> 00:31:05,640
you know, and then it kicks in.

726
00:31:05,640 --> 00:31:06,760
Are you saying my...

727
00:31:06,760 --> 00:31:07,600
Let's drop this topic.

728
00:31:07,600 --> 00:31:08,530
But don't worry.

729
00:31:08,680 --> 00:31:10,320
He definitely didn't eat your kidneys for nothing.

730
00:31:10,320 --> 00:31:11,080
He is

731
00:31:11,080 --> 00:31:12,010
a man of his word.

732
00:31:12,920 --> 00:31:14,380
Let's not advertise that.

733
00:31:27,120 --> 00:31:29,840
I heard you're performing a solo dance on New Year's Day.

734
00:31:29,840 --> 00:31:30,360
Get out.

735
00:31:31,240 --> 00:31:33,040
I absolutely have to show off.

736
00:31:34,320 --> 00:31:35,320
I've studied dance for six years

737
00:31:35,320 --> 00:31:36,520
and still don't dare to perform solo.

738
00:31:36,520 --> 00:31:37,600
How do you dare?

739
00:31:37,800 --> 00:31:39,520
Even if I had studied seriously for one day.

740
00:31:39,520 --> 00:31:41,850
My uncle never studied law for a single day

741
00:31:41,880 --> 00:31:43,160
but he's still taking the bar exam.

742
00:31:43,160 --> 00:31:44,040
My dad taking the bar exam

743
00:31:44,040 --> 00:31:45,440
doesn't have to perform in public.

744
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:47,760
You're just making a fool of yourself in public.

745
00:31:47,760 --> 00:31:48,880
When you shake like that,

746
00:31:48,880 --> 00:31:49,800
the flesh on your cheeks

747
00:31:49,800 --> 00:31:51,160
will jiggle for ages.

748
00:31:52,600 --> 00:31:54,800
That's what gives it rhythm and impact.

749
00:31:56,040 --> 00:31:57,200
I'm begging you,

750
00:31:57,200 --> 00:31:58,520
please don't dance.

751
00:31:58,600 --> 00:31:59,600
Many of my classmates

752
00:31:59,600 --> 00:32:01,040
already know you're my cousin.

753
00:32:01,040 --> 00:32:01,880
If you really dance,

754
00:32:01,880 --> 00:32:03,160
how am I supposed to live with that?

755
00:32:03,160 --> 00:32:05,360
You'll live with dignity because of me.

756
00:32:05,520 --> 00:32:06,320
Well then,

757
00:32:06,320 --> 00:32:07,760
show me a dance first.

758
00:32:07,920 --> 00:32:09,400
I haven't learned it yet.

759
00:32:09,600 --> 00:32:11,260
Then what are you dancing for?

760
00:32:12,600 --> 00:32:14,040
You have to believe in my potential.

761
00:32:14,040 --> 00:32:15,160
When pushed to the limit,

762
00:32:15,160 --> 00:32:16,240
I can do anything.

763
00:32:18,680 --> 00:32:20,080
Even if you were pushed to death,

764
00:32:20,080 --> 00:32:22,010
could you solve this math problem?

765
00:32:23,840 --> 00:32:25,440
I support you, Erpang.

766
00:32:25,960 --> 00:32:27,840
Snow weighs down bamboo branches,

767
00:32:27,840 --> 00:32:29,300
bending them near the mud.

768
00:32:29,640 --> 00:32:31,160
But when the sun rises,

769
00:32:31,640 --> 00:32:33,900
they stand tall again, reaching the sky.

770
00:32:35,760 --> 00:32:37,020
Your current hardship

771
00:32:37,160 --> 00:32:39,360
doesn't mean you'll struggle forever.

772
00:32:39,640 --> 00:32:41,240
Don't forget when you were little,

773
00:32:41,240 --> 00:32:43,240
you won the crawling championship.

774
00:32:43,440 --> 00:32:44,240
Keep going.

775
00:32:45,280 --> 00:32:46,610
Everyone, be quiet now.

776
00:32:52,800 --> 00:32:54,720
Thank you for your hard work.

777
00:32:55,480 --> 00:32:56,880
If it weren't for you,

778
00:32:57,320 --> 00:32:58,280
how could I

779
00:32:58,280 --> 00:33:00,440
have arranged a meeting with the factory director?

780
00:33:00,440 --> 00:33:02,600
It's not hard to invite him for a meal.

781
00:33:03,800 --> 00:33:04,880
But

782
00:33:05,400 --> 00:33:06,800
why do you want to see him?

783
00:33:07,240 --> 00:33:08,200
It's about

784
00:33:08,480 --> 00:33:10,360
my son, Cui Guoming.

785
00:33:10,360 --> 00:33:11,360
Guoming?

786
00:33:13,000 --> 00:33:14,530
He's known for being smart.

787
00:33:15,400 --> 00:33:16,200
Everyone knows

788
00:33:16,200 --> 00:33:18,200
he was a good student when he was young.

789
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:20,660
Didn't he go to the Engineering University?

790
00:33:20,880 --> 00:33:22,480
What could be wrong with him?

791
00:33:22,960 --> 00:33:24,360
Nothing serious.

792
00:33:24,920 --> 00:33:26,520
He's just not steady enough,

793
00:33:26,600 --> 00:33:28,440
always has too many ideas.

794
00:33:29,080 --> 00:33:30,920
When the old factory director was around,

795
00:33:30,920 --> 00:33:32,480
he was pampered and spoiled,

796
00:33:32,480 --> 00:33:34,000
and life was decent.

797
00:33:34,280 --> 00:33:35,880
But when the new director arrived,

798
00:33:35,880 --> 00:33:38,080
how could he tolerate someone like him?

799
00:33:38,880 --> 00:33:41,480
He's been suspended for self-reflection now.

800
00:33:41,800 --> 00:33:43,060
But I've talked to him.

801
00:33:43,760 --> 00:33:45,680
He'll work properly from now on.

802
00:33:46,160 --> 00:33:47,800
When the director comes,

803
00:33:47,800 --> 00:33:49,880
please put in a good word for him.

804
00:33:52,160 --> 00:33:53,680
We've been friends for decades.

805
00:33:53,680 --> 00:33:54,760
I'll certainly do my best.

806
00:33:54,760 --> 00:33:55,200
Good.

807
00:33:58,800 --> 00:33:59,360
Sir,

808
00:34:00,680 --> 00:34:01,940
I'm late for a meeting.

809
00:34:03,640 --> 00:34:05,280
And you're treating me to a meal.

810
00:34:05,280 --> 00:34:07,240
This is really too kind of you.

811
00:34:07,440 --> 00:34:09,480
I've always wanted to treat you to dinner

812
00:34:09,480 --> 00:34:11,360
to thank you for all these years

813
00:34:11,360 --> 00:34:13,360
of mentoring me.

814
00:34:14,840 --> 00:34:16,040
Let me introduce you.

815
00:34:16,280 --> 00:34:19,320
This is General Manager Cui from Dingqing Restaurant.

816
00:34:19,320 --> 00:34:20,719
Former general manager.

817
00:34:20,920 --> 00:34:21,840
I just retired.

818
00:34:21,960 --> 00:34:23,560
I've heard so much about you.

819
00:34:23,560 --> 00:34:24,840
Please, have a seat.

820
00:34:25,159 --> 00:34:26,400
Sit down.

821
00:34:26,400 --> 00:34:26,560
Okay.

822
00:34:26,560 --> 00:34:27,280
Come.

823
00:34:31,920 --> 00:34:32,880
Have a seat.

824
00:34:34,320 --> 00:34:35,120
Please sit down.

825
00:34:35,120 --> 00:34:36,179
Please take a seat.

826
00:34:36,440 --> 00:34:37,280
Sit down.

827
00:34:39,960 --> 00:34:40,560
Alright.

828
00:34:42,199 --> 00:34:44,280
You've just taken office recently.

829
00:34:44,280 --> 00:34:45,679
Must be quite busy.

830
00:34:46,440 --> 00:34:48,239
Don't even mention it, sir.

831
00:34:48,239 --> 00:34:49,770
I've got a heap of problems.

832
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:51,120
The company has been

833
00:34:51,120 --> 00:34:52,520
losing money for 4 years.

834
00:34:53,280 --> 00:34:56,000
The higher-ups want us to cut staff.

835
00:34:57,160 --> 00:34:58,000
I just arrived

836
00:34:58,000 --> 00:34:59,360
and immediately face this thankless task.

837
00:34:59,360 --> 00:35:00,690
What am I supposed to do?

838
00:35:01,200 --> 00:35:02,840
So layoffs have reached your factory now.

839
00:35:02,840 --> 00:35:03,760
That's right.

840
00:35:04,200 --> 00:35:05,760
We're the first to face it.

841
00:35:06,360 --> 00:35:08,840
Our factory's revenue is average,

842
00:35:09,160 --> 00:35:11,320
but we have the most employees in the city.

843
00:35:11,320 --> 00:35:12,380
Tens of thousands.

844
00:35:13,600 --> 00:35:16,320
That's tens of thousands of families.

845
00:35:16,960 --> 00:35:18,880
I just arrived

846
00:35:18,880 --> 00:35:20,440
and they make me do this.

847
00:35:21,720 --> 00:35:23,800
It's definitely not easy.

848
00:35:25,000 --> 00:35:26,200
I also want to use this opportunity

849
00:35:26,200 --> 00:35:27,730
to reorganize the factory.

850
00:35:28,040 --> 00:35:29,320
For example, our factory

851
00:35:29,320 --> 00:35:30,600
has a troublemaker.

852
00:35:30,840 --> 00:35:32,700
He never takes his job seriously.

853
00:35:32,720 --> 00:35:34,280
Always coming in late or leaving early.

854
00:35:34,280 --> 00:35:35,120
And the office?

855
00:35:35,120 --> 00:35:36,920
He's turned it into a complete mess.

856
00:35:36,920 --> 00:35:39,360
You put him on suspension,

857
00:35:39,360 --> 00:35:42,000
and what does he do? Goes to nightclubs to sing.

858
00:35:42,600 --> 00:35:43,640
And that's not all.

859
00:35:43,640 --> 00:35:44,760
He spends all his time

860
00:35:44,760 --> 00:35:46,520
hanging out with those shady characters

861
