871
00:36:02,440 --> 00:36:03,170
Cui Guoming.

872
00:36:03,240 --> 00:36:04,360
Yes, Cui Guoming.

873
00:36:05,320 --> 00:36:06,600
The day we settle the severance packages,

874
00:36:06,600 --> 00:36:07,760
he'll be the first to go.

875
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:09,840
Our management team has reached a consensus.

876
00:36:09,840 --> 00:36:11,400
For people like him,

877
00:36:11,400 --> 00:36:13,560
no amount of pleading will help.

878
00:36:14,680 --> 00:36:16,280
If he doesn't go, who should?

879
00:36:17,920 --> 00:36:19,780
Hurry up and serve the hot dishes.

880
00:36:30,120 --> 00:36:31,120
So everyone

881
00:36:32,040 --> 00:36:33,600
has been invited, right?

882
00:36:34,400 --> 00:36:35,660
What about the drinks?

883
00:36:36,720 --> 00:36:38,520
Everyone's had enough to drink.

884
00:36:39,680 --> 00:36:42,080
Why won't you let me speak?

885
00:36:42,360 --> 00:36:44,920
I can't lose face like that.

886
00:36:45,920 --> 00:36:48,850
Between us old friends, there's nothing more to say.

887
00:36:49,960 --> 00:36:50,420
This...

888
00:36:50,560 --> 00:36:51,080
This...

889
00:36:51,920 --> 00:36:52,960
I...

890
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:56,840
I can't put you in a difficult position.

891
00:36:57,200 --> 00:36:58,880
You know what,

892
00:36:59,560 --> 00:37:01,360
you're too thin-skinned.

893
00:37:04,240 --> 00:37:06,080
Isn't this drink going to waste?

894
00:37:06,080 --> 00:37:08,560
No, not at all.

895
00:37:09,200 --> 00:37:10,440
The two of us

896
00:37:10,440 --> 00:37:12,280
have already drunk it, haven't we?

897
00:37:12,280 --> 00:37:12,720
Right?

898
00:37:23,160 --> 00:37:24,520
Slow down.

899
00:37:31,960 --> 00:37:32,840
Ji Qiang.

900
00:37:32,840 --> 00:37:34,200
It's getting cold.

901
00:37:34,200 --> 00:37:37,000
Go back and get some sleep.

902
00:37:43,880 --> 00:37:44,720
This time

903
00:37:45,200 --> 00:37:47,060
it coincided with the crackdown.

904
00:37:47,560 --> 00:37:49,080
Plus, he's a celebrity,

905
00:37:49,080 --> 00:37:50,560
so who else would they arrest?

906
00:37:50,560 --> 00:37:51,890
Look at someone like me,

907
00:37:52,200 --> 00:37:54,400
detained for 15 days and then released.

908
00:37:57,560 --> 00:38:00,820
Actually, I came to see you today for something important.

909
00:38:01,160 --> 00:38:02,760
Brother Huo told me

910
00:38:02,760 --> 00:38:04,640
to give you this money.

911
00:38:04,640 --> 00:38:06,360
You need money to raise Erpang.

912
00:38:06,360 --> 00:38:07,160
Take it.

913
00:38:08,160 --> 00:38:09,360
Erpang.

914
00:38:10,080 --> 00:38:11,880
We can afford to take care of him.

915
00:38:11,880 --> 00:38:12,680
We don't need this money.

916
00:38:12,680 --> 00:38:14,080
You should let him quickly.

917
00:38:14,080 --> 00:38:14,760
No, no, no.

918
00:38:15,080 --> 00:38:16,720
If it weren't for Brother Huo,

919
00:38:16,720 --> 00:38:18,440
I wouldn't have earned this money, right?

920
00:38:18,440 --> 00:38:19,720
Just let him use it

921
00:38:19,720 --> 00:38:21,440
to improve his meals in there.

922
00:38:22,360 --> 00:38:23,040
Take it back first.

923
00:38:23,040 --> 00:38:24,280
Really, take it back.

924
00:38:26,760 --> 00:38:28,440
Actually, we earn quite a lot.

925
00:38:28,800 --> 00:38:30,080
While he's in there,

926
00:38:31,160 --> 00:38:32,320
the money I earn

927
00:38:32,320 --> 00:38:33,160
is his too.

928
00:38:33,320 --> 00:38:34,520
Yes, didn't I tell you?

929
00:38:34,520 --> 00:38:35,960
If you keep acting like this,

930
00:38:35,960 --> 00:38:37,440
I'm going to get angry with you.

931
00:38:37,440 --> 00:38:38,880
Just stop explaining all this.

932
00:38:38,880 --> 00:38:41,440
Fine, I'll keep it for now.

933
00:38:43,080 --> 00:38:45,240
When are you going back to work?

934
00:38:46,960 --> 00:38:47,960
I don't want to work there anymore.

935
00:38:47,960 --> 00:38:50,080
Why? It's such a good job.

936
00:38:51,160 --> 00:38:52,880
I have bigger plans.

937
00:40:12,280 --> 00:40:13,600
Today's meal

938
00:40:14,440 --> 00:40:15,720
is quite good.

939
00:40:16,560 --> 00:40:17,440
Actually,

940
00:40:17,880 --> 00:40:19,720
if you study seriously,

941
00:40:20,440 --> 00:40:23,040
you could become a chef at Dingqing Restaurant.

942
00:40:23,040 --> 00:40:24,200
It's possible.

943
00:40:24,400 --> 00:40:25,880
You have the talent.

944
00:40:25,880 --> 00:40:26,880
Why would I become a chef?

945
00:40:26,880 --> 00:40:28,810
Dad, I'm trying to become a lawyer.

946
00:40:29,000 --> 00:40:30,560
But you haven't passed the exam yet.

947
00:40:30,560 --> 00:40:31,280
I didn't pass,

948
00:40:31,280 --> 00:40:32,680
but I did extremely well.

949
00:40:32,880 --> 00:40:33,880
It was perfect,

950
00:40:33,880 --> 00:40:35,160
flawless.

951
00:40:36,040 --> 00:40:37,100
What are you doing?

952
00:40:37,120 --> 00:40:37,840
All my life,

953
00:40:37,840 --> 00:40:38,480
I...

954
00:40:38,480 --> 00:40:40,010
you can say I'm unreliable,

955
00:40:40,120 --> 00:40:41,720
but when it comes to exams,

956
00:40:41,840 --> 00:40:43,300
who dares say I'm not good?

957
00:40:43,320 --> 00:40:44,440
That's true.

958
00:40:44,760 --> 00:40:46,720
But it will be

959
00:40:46,720 --> 00:40:48,980
a few months before the results come out.

960
00:40:49,400 --> 00:40:52,000
The factory won't take you back,

961
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:54,400
so what do you plan to do during this time?

962
00:40:57,200 --> 00:40:58,920
After studying for a while,

963
00:40:59,160 --> 00:41:00,400
I feel that I

964
00:41:00,720 --> 00:41:01,720
am really suited for

965
00:41:01,720 --> 00:41:02,760
desk work.

966
00:41:04,480 --> 00:41:05,720
I want to

967
00:41:05,720 --> 00:41:08,280
write a popular martial arts novel.

968
00:41:10,720 --> 00:41:12,160
I've even thought of a pen name,

969
00:41:12,160 --> 00:41:14,720
Gu Longju.

970
00:41:15,920 --> 00:41:17,440
When my book is published,

971
00:41:17,560 --> 00:41:20,020
it will be called 'A Great Work by Gu Longju.'

972
00:41:22,880 --> 00:41:24,880
I have a high school classmate who works at a publishing house.

973
00:41:24,880 --> 00:41:26,640
He says I have real talent.

974
00:41:26,640 --> 00:41:27,720
I can write too.

975
00:41:27,720 --> 00:41:28,920
And with my skills,

976
00:41:28,920 --> 00:41:30,520
I could finish a book in just one month.

977
00:41:30,520 --> 00:41:31,080
Each book

978
00:41:31,080 --> 00:41:32,160
would earn me 5,000 yuan.

979
00:41:32,160 --> 00:41:32,880
Just think about it. In a month,

980
00:41:32,880 --> 00:41:33,720
I could make 5,000 yuan.

981
00:41:33,720 --> 00:41:36,320
That's way better than working at the factory.

982
00:41:36,440 --> 00:41:37,960
I don't object to this.

983
00:41:39,720 --> 00:41:41,720
You're just sitting around anyway,

984
00:41:42,200 --> 00:41:44,720
better than going out and causing trouble.

985
00:41:45,280 --> 00:41:46,840
But let's be clear.

986
00:41:47,280 --> 00:41:49,840
If you write, do it quietly.

987
00:41:50,320 --> 00:41:51,440
No going out.

988
00:41:51,720 --> 00:41:53,200
If you finish it, great.

989
00:41:53,280 --> 00:41:55,280
If not, that's fine too.

990
00:41:55,280 --> 00:41:58,080
If the factory calls you back to work,

991
00:41:58,280 --> 00:41:59,940
you must return immediately.

992
00:42:05,280 --> 00:42:06,040
That's right, Dad.

993
00:42:06,040 --> 00:42:06,960
I can

994
00:42:06,960 --> 00:42:08,760
give everyone a brief introduction to

995
00:42:08,760 --> 00:42:10,880
the origins of martial arts novels.

996
00:42:12,320 --> 00:42:14,040
In Macau in the 1950s,

997
00:42:14,280 --> 00:42:15,200
they organized a

998
00:42:15,200 --> 00:42:16,730
martial arts competition.

999
00:42:17,640 --> 00:42:20,300
That competition was absolutely unwatchable.

1000
00:42:20,320 --> 00:42:22,160
They were just throwing wild punches,

1001
00:42:22,160 --> 00:42:23,640
with no skill whatsoever,

1002
00:42:23,640 --> 00:42:24,770
no technique at all.

1003
00:42:25,840 --> 00:42:27,300
But this very competition

1004
00:42:27,400 --> 00:42:28,640
inspired a reporter from Ta Kung Pao newspaper

1005
00:42:28,640 --> 00:42:29,770
to write something.

1006
00:42:29,840 --> 00:42:31,400
His name was Liang Yusheng,

1007
00:42:31,840 --> 00:42:33,280
and he wrote a novel

1008
00:42:33,520 --> 00:42:35,960
called 'Dragon and Tiger Fight in Beijing.'

1009
00:42:35,960 --> 00:42:37,160
It became an instant hit.

1010
00:42:37,160 --> 00:42:38,960
This Liang Yusheng had a buddy

1011
00:42:39,160 --> 00:42:40,520
named Cha Liangyong.

1012
00:42:41,040 --> 00:42:42,520
When Cha Liangyong saw Liang's success,

1013
00:42:42,520 --> 00:42:42,960
he couldn't stand it.

1014
00:42:42,960 --> 00:42:44,020
He wanted fame too.

1015
00:42:44,200 --> 00:42:45,400
So he wrote

1016
00:42:45,400 --> 00:42:46,960
'The Book and the Sword.'

1017
00:42:47,600 --> 00:42:48,320
Eventually,

1018
00:42:48,320 --> 00:42:49,320
he took his name, Cha Liangyong,

1019
00:42:49,320 --> 00:42:51,040
and split the last character 'yong' apart

1020
00:42:51,040 --> 00:42:52,400
to create his pen name.

1021
00:42:52,400 --> 00:42:53,760
He became Jin Yong.

